{"tid":389420,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩會員:對唔住都係我 入黎商討約戰事宜！","createTime":"2017-09-06T08:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T11:34:39.000Z","uid":54025,"like":11,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7052f1df4d007e9e0e4a4d2c226c7e015b82299","tid":389420,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:56:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/384304/page/2?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/384304/page/2?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n如題，依個post 大家意見不合，打算訴武力，但其實本人都係講下笑<br />\n<br />\n但估唔到真係有柒頭咁撚上心要我找數<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/384304/page/2?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/384304/page/2?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n當日我曾經害到會員世界情色王比人笑粒水。所以佢一直懷恨於心，好想做鳩我咁話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/165420_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F165420_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=db57c5b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/165426_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F165426_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c6b5acb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實開頭都唔係好想理佢，但奈何條撚樣真係太煩，所以只好出黎找左條數佢叫佢唔好再煩我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以有勞巴打入黎講低時間地點幾時方便。<br />\n不過如果巴打都係一時玩玩其實無心打既就無謂滿足班柒頭而出黎了。<br />\n但如果巴打真係好想切磋既，本人樂意奉陪，打完大家渣渣手食個宵夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請盡快回覆，多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add5ea8aee1df13837686e6dc0a0f7af586e878a","tid":389420,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ohzAH4tGyDZasUzF6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3ohzAH4tGyDZasUzF6%2Fgiphy.gif&h=f8565989&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e6a3d0e0166216dc321376313cabc4d49b83ddd","tid":389420,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ohzAH4tGyDZasUzF6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3ohzAH4tGyDZasUzF6%2Fgiphy.gif&h=f8565989&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88663960d3115fc6931ab8d33960b4b01ef97d36","tid":389420,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:58:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ohzAH4tGyDZasUzF6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3ohzAH4tGyDZasUzF6%2Fgiphy.gif&h=f8565989&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d67b395fc00c554b5844d16cfac2eb6a3b4383b8","tid":389420,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:58:28.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"a191ee9cbdc2738d76072f96af3d902804ee1ca8","tid":389420,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"世狗仲有咩講！？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ohzAH4tGyDZasUzF6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3ohzAH4tGyDZasUzF6%2Fgiphy.gif&h=f8565989&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4338416eb4d7f889520206cb2fb4b52b5d2278b","tid":389420,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:01:00.000Z","msg":"支持，我願意提供贊助"},{"pid":"c6ea115550ba75f5cd25ad473a81ad2dcfe0ac0f","tid":389420,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:01:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>世狗仲有咩講！？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ohzAH4tGyDZasUzF6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn